    "html_format": "<div class=\"document-view-wrapper\">\n<style>\n.html-preview * {font-family: Times New Roman; font-size: 12pt;}\n.html-preview a.NoteRef {text-decoration: none;}\n.html-preview table td {vertical-align: top;}\n.html-preview table {width: 100%;}\n.html-preview p {white-space: pre-wrap;}\n.html-preview .leading {width: 4px; display: inline-block;}\n.html-preview hr {height: 1px; padding: 0; margin: 1em 0; border: 0; border-top: 1px solid #CCC;}\n.html-preview .Normal {className: Normal; margin-bottom: 8pt;}\n.html-preview .a {font-family: 'Calibri';}\n.html-preview .ConsPlusNonformat {font-family: 'Courier New'; font-size: 10pt;}\n.html-preview .a3 {font-family: 'Times New Roman';}\n</style>\n<div class=\"html-preview\">\n<style>.html-preview{width: 762px}</style><style>.html-preview{margin-top: 76px}</style><style>.html-preview{margin-bottom: 32px}</style><style>.html-preview{padding-left: 81px}</style><style>.html-preview{padding-right: 57px}</style><table>\n<tr>\n<td 0=\"\" style=\" width: 311.86703601108px;\">\n<p> </p>\n</td>\n<td 0=\"\" style=\" width: 324.43213296399px;\">\n<p style=\"text-align: justify; margin-bottom: 0pt;\"><span style=\"font-family: 'Times New Roman'; font-size: 14pt; font-weight: bold;\">Фуқаролик ишлари бўйича </span><span class=\"structures structure-2\" style=\"font-family: 'Times New Roman'; font-size: 14pt; font-weight: bold;\">{#2}Ариза берилган фуқаролик суди номи</span><span style=\"font-family: 'Times New Roman'; font-size: 14pt; font-weight: bold;\"> судига</span></p>\n<p> </p>\n</td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td 1=\"\" style=\" width: 311.86703601108px;\">\n<p> </p>\n</td>\n<td 1=\"\" style=\" width: 324.43213296399px;\">\n<p style=\"text-align: justify; margin-bottom: 0pt;\"><span style=\"font-family: 'Times New Roman'; font-size: 14pt;\"> </span><span class=\"structures structure-5\" style=\"font-family: 'Times New Roman'; font-size: 14pt;\">{#5}Аризачининг яшаш манзили</span><span style=\"font-family: 'Times New Roman'; font-size: 14pt;\">да яшовчи</span></p>\n</td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td 2=\"\" style=\" width: 311.86703601108px;\">\n<p> </p>\n</td>\n<td 2=\"\" style=\" width: 324.43213296399px;\">\n<p style=\"text-align: justify; margin-bottom: 0pt;\"><span class=\"structures structure-6\" style=\"font-family: 'Times New Roman'; font-size: 14pt;\">{#6}Аризачининг Ф.И.О.си</span><span style=\"font-family: 'Times New Roman'; font-size: 14pt;\"> томонидан</span></p>\n</td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td 3=\"\" style=\" width: 311.86703601108px;\">\n<p> </p>\n</td>\n<td 3=\"\" style=\" width: 324.43213296399px;\">\n<p style=\"text-align: justify; margin-bottom: 0pt;\"><span style=\"font-family: 'Times New Roman'; font-size: 14pt;\">Телефон: </span><span class=\"structures structure-7\" style=\"font-family: 'Times New Roman'; font-size: 14pt;\">{#7}Аризачининг телефон рақами</span></p>\n<p style=\"text-align: justify; margin-bottom: 0pt;\"><span style=\"font-family: 'Times New Roman'; font-size: 14pt;\">E-mail: </span><span class=\"structures structure-8\" style=\"font-family: 'Times New Roman'; font-size: 14pt;\">{#8}Аризачининг E-mail манзили</span></p>\n</td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td 4=\"\" style=\" width: 311.86703601108px;\">\n<p> </p>\n</td>\n<td 4=\"\" style=\" width: 324.43213296399px;\">\n<p> </p>\n</td>\n</tr>\n</table>\n<p class=\"ConsPlusNonformat\" style=\" text-align: center;\"><span style=\"font-family: 'Times New Roman'; font-size: 14pt; font-weight: bold;\">АРИЗА</span></p>\n<p class=\"ConsPlusNonformat\" style=\" text-align: center;\"><span style=\"font-family: 'Times New Roman'; font-size: 14pt;\">(суд буйруғини бекор қилиш ҳақида)</span></p>\n<p> </p>\n<p class=\"ConsPlusNonformat\" style=\" text-align: justify;\"><span class=\"tab\" style=\"width: 47.2px; display: inline-block\"></span><span style=\"font-family: 'Times New Roman'; font-size: 14pt;\"> Фуқаролик ишлари бўйича </span><span class=\"structures structure-10\" style=\"font-family: 'Times New Roman'; font-size: 14pt;\">{#10}Суд буйруғи қабул қилган суд номи </span><span style=\"font-family: 'Times New Roman'; font-size: 14pt;\"> судининг <span class=\"leading\"></span></span><span class=\"structures structure-11\" style=\"font-family: 'Times New Roman'; font-size: 14pt;\">{#11}Суд буйруғи қабул қилинган сана</span><span style=\"font-family: 'Times New Roman'; font-size: 14pt;\">даги <span class=\"leading\"></span></span><span class=\"structures structure-12\" style=\"font-family: 'Times New Roman'; font-size: 14pt;\">{#12}Қабул қилинган суд буйруғининг рақами</span><span style=\"font-family: 'Times New Roman'; font-size: 14pt;\">-сонли суд буйруғига асосан мендан </span><span class=\"structures structure-13\" style=\"font-family: 'Times New Roman'; font-size: 14pt;\">{#13}Суд буйруғига асосан фойдасига моддий таъминот ундириш белгиланган боланинг <span class=\"leading\"></span>туғулган санаси </span><span style=\"font-family: 'Times New Roman'; font-size: 14pt;\">да туғилган <span class=\"leading\"></span>вояга етмаган <span class=\"leading\"></span><span class=\"leading\"></span></span><span class=\"structures structure-14\" style=\"font-family: 'Times New Roman'; font-size: 14pt;\">{#14}Суд буйруғига асосан фойдасига моддий таъминот ундириш белгиланган боланинг <span class=\"leading\"></span>Ф.И.Ш.си</span><span style=\"font-family: 'Times New Roman'; font-size: 14pt;\"> исмли боланинг моддий таъминоти учун алимент ундириш белгиланиб, </span><span class=\"structures structure-15\" style=\"font-family: 'Times New Roman'; font-size: 14pt;\">{#15}Суд буйруғи чиқарилиши тўғрисида ариза берган шахснинг Ф.И.Ш.и </span><span style=\"font-family: 'Times New Roman'; font-size: 14pt;\">нинг аризаси қаноатлантирилган. <span class=\"leading\"></span>Мен ушбу суд буйруғи қабул қилинган суд жараёнида қатнашмаганман. </span></p>\n<p class=\"ConsPlusNonformat\" style=\" text-align: justify; text-indent: 47.2px;\"><span style=\"font-family: 'Times New Roman'; font-size: 14pt;\">Ўзбекистон Республикаси Фуқаролик процессуал кодексининг 170-моддасига кўра, суд буйруғи низосиз талаблар бўйича суд муҳокамаси ўтказмасдан бериладиган суд ҳужжатидир. </span></p>\n<p class=\"ConsPlusNonformat\" style=\" text-align: justify; text-indent: 47.266666666667px;\"><span style=\"font-family: 'Times New Roman'; font-size: 14pt;\">Мен ва суд буйруғи қабул қилинишида аризачи сифатида қатнашган </span><span class=\"structures structure-15\" style=\"font-family: 'Times New Roman'; font-size: 14pt;\">{#15}Суд буйруғи чиқарилиши тўғрисида ариза берган шахснинг Ф.И.Ш.и </span><span style=\"font-family: 'Times New Roman'; font-size: 14pt;\">ўртамизда </span><span class=\"structures structure-13\" style=\"font-family: 'Times New Roman'; font-size: 14pt;\">{#13}Суд буйруғига асосан фойдасига моддий таъминот ундириш белгиланган боланинг <span class=\"leading\"></span>туғулган санаси </span><span style=\"font-family: 'Times New Roman'; font-size: 14pt;\">да туғилган вояга етмаган </span><span class=\"structures structure-14\" style=\"font-family: 'Times New Roman'; font-size: 14pt;\">{#14}Суд буйруғига асосан фойдасига моддий таъминот ундириш белгиланган боланинг <span class=\"leading\"></span>Ф.И.Ш.си</span><span style=\"font-family: 'Times New Roman'; font-size: 14pt;\">га оталикни белгилаш масаласида низо мавжуд. Мен </span><span class=\"structures structure-14\" style=\"font-family: 'Times New Roman'; font-size: 14pt;\">{#14}Суд буйруғига асосан фойдасига моддий таъминот ундириш белгиланган боланинг <span class=\"leading\"></span>Ф.И.Ш.си</span><span style=\"font-family: 'Times New Roman'; font-size: 14pt;\">ни ўз фарзандим деб билмайман. </span></p>\n<p class=\"ConsPlusNonformat\" style=\" text-align: justify; text-indent: 47.266666666667px;\"><span style=\"font-family: 'Times New Roman'; font-size: 14pt;\"> <span class=\"leading\"></span>Фуқаролик процессуал кодексининг 181-моддасига кўра, қарздор арз қилинган талабга қарши эътирозларини буйруқни берган судга беради. Алимент ундириш тўғрисидаги суд буйруғи ижро ишини юритиш бўйича ундирув тугагунига қадар ундирувчининг аризасига кўра бекор қилиниши мумкин. Бундай ҳолда судъя суд буйруғини бекор қилиб, бу ҳақида ажрим чиқаради. <span class=\"leading\"></span></span></p>\n<p class=\"ConsPlusNonformat\" style=\" text-align: justify; text-indent: 47.266666666667px;\"><span style=\"font-family: 'Times New Roman'; font-size: 14pt;\"> Юқоридагиларга кўра, Ўзбекистон Республикаси Фуқаролик процессуал <span class=\"leading\"></span>Кодексининг 3, 4, 170, 181, 189-моддаларига асосан </span></p>\n<p> </p>\n<p class=\"ConsPlusNonformat\" style=\" text-align: center;\"><span style=\"font-family: 'Times New Roman'; font-size: 14pt; font-weight: bold;\">СЎРАЙМАН:</span></p>\n<p> </p>\n<p class=\"ConsPlusNonformat\" style=\" text-align: justify;\"><span style=\"font-family: 'Times New Roman'; font-size: 14pt;\"> </span><span class=\"tab\" style=\"width: 47.2px; display: inline-block\"></span><span style=\"font-family: 'Times New Roman'; font-size: 14pt;\">Фуқаролик ишлари бўйича </span><span class=\"structures structure-10\" style=\"font-family: 'Times New Roman'; font-size: 14pt;\">{#10}Суд буйруғи қабул қилган суд номи </span><span style=\"font-family: 'Times New Roman'; font-size: 14pt;\"> судининг </span><span class=\"structures structure-11\" style=\"font-family: 'Times New Roman'; font-size: 14pt;\">{#11}Суд буйруғи қабул қилинган сана</span><span style=\"font-family: 'Times New Roman'; font-size: 14pt;\">даги <span class=\"leading\"></span></span><span class=\"structures structure-15\" style=\"font-family: 'Times New Roman'; font-size: 14pt;\">{#15}Суд буйруғи чиқарилиши тўғрисида ариза берган шахснинг Ф.И.Ш.и </span><span style=\"font-family: 'Times New Roman'; font-size: 14pt;\">фойдасига </span><span class=\"structures structure-13\" style=\"font-family: 'Times New Roman'; font-size: 14pt;\">{#13}Суд буйруғига асосан фойдасига моддий таъминот ундириш белгиланган боланинг <span class=\"leading\"></span>туғулган санаси </span><span style=\"font-family: 'Times New Roman'; font-size: 14pt;\">да туғилган </span><span class=\"structures structure-14\" style=\"font-family: 'Times New Roman'; font-size: 14pt;\">{#14}Суд буйруғига асосан фойдасига моддий таъминот ундириш белгиланган боланинг <span class=\"leading\"></span>Ф.И.Ш.си</span><span style=\"font-family: 'Times New Roman'; font-size: 14pt;\"> исмли боланинг моддий таъминоти учун алимент ундириш ҳақидаги </span><span class=\"structures structure-12\" style=\"font-family: 'Times New Roman'; font-size: 14pt;\">{#12}Қабул қилинган суд буйруғининг рақами</span><span style=\"font-family: 'Times New Roman'; font-size: 14pt;\">-<span class=\"leading\"></span>сонли суд буйруғини бекор қилишингизни. </span></p>\n<p> </p>\n<p class=\"ConsPlusNonformat\" style=\" text-align: justify;\"><span style=\"font-family: 'Times New Roman'; font-size: 14pt; font-weight: bold;\"> <span class=\"leading\"></span><span class=\"leading\"></span><span class=\"leading\"></span><span class=\"leading\"></span><span class=\"leading\"></span><span class=\"leading\"></span><span class=\"leading\"></span><span class=\"leading\"></span><span class=\"leading\"></span>Илова:</span></p>\n<p class=\"ConsPlusNonformat\" style=\" text-align: justify;\"><span style=\"font-family: 'Times New Roman'; font-size: 14pt;\"> <span class=\"leading\"></span><span class=\"leading\"></span><span class=\"leading\"></span>1. Суд буйруғи нусхаси.</span></p>\n<p class=\"ConsPlusNonformat\" style=\" text-align: justify;\"><span style=\"font-family: 'Times New Roman'; font-size: 14pt;\"> <span class=\"leading\"></span><span class=\"leading\"></span><span class=\"leading\"></span>2. Аризамни асословчи ҳужжатлар. <span class=\"leading\"></span><span class=\"leading\"></span><span class=\"leading\"></span></span></p>\n<p> </p>\n<p class=\"ConsPlusNonformat\" style=\" text-align: justify;\"><span style=\"font-family: 'Times New Roman'; font-size: 14pt; font-weight: bold;\">Даъвогар <span class=\"leading\"></span></span><span class=\"structures structure-6\" style=\"font-family: 'Times New Roman'; font-size: 14pt; font-weight: bold;\">{#6}Аризачининг Ф.И.О.си</span><span style=\"font-family: 'Times New Roman'; font-size: 14pt; font-weight: bold;\"> <span class=\"leading\"></span><span class=\"leading\"></span><span class=\"leading\"></span><span class=\"leading\"></span><span class=\"leading\"></span></span><span style=\"font-family: 'Times New Roman'; font-size: 14pt; font-style: italic;\"> <span class=\"leading\"></span><span class=\"leading\"></span><span class=\"leading\"></span><span class=\"leading\"></span><span class=\"leading\"></span><span class=\"leading\"></span><span class=\"leading\"></span><span class=\"leading\"></span><span class=\"leading\"></span><span class=\"leading\"></span><span class=\"leading\"></span><span class=\"leading\"></span><span class=\"leading\"></span></span><span class=\"structures structure-3\" style=\"font-family: 'Times New Roman'; font-size: 14pt; font-weight: bold;\">{#3}Ариза берилган сана</span><span style=\"font-family: 'Times New Roman'; font-size: 14pt; font-weight: bold;\"> <span class=\"leading\"></span><span class=\"leading\"></span><span class=\"leading\"></span><span class=\"leading\"></span><span class=\"leading\"></span><span class=\"leading\"></span><span class=\"leading\"></span><span class=\"leading\"></span><span class=\"leading\"></span><span class=\"leading\"></span></span></p>\n<p> </p>\n<p> </p>\n<p> </p>\n<p> </p>\n</div></div>",
